    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The CFD model is judged credible for its intended use: identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index satisfies RH < 1 at all five evaluated operating points. The credibility assessment team accepts the model for regulatory submission in support of the Class II CPB device 510(k) application.",
